					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9775712#post-4104188</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9775712/the-doctor-s-dilemma#post-4104188</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 31 Dec 2018 12:13:50 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Glypshmergle</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4897243</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Damn that shit got me pretty good.</p> <p>These and all the other tales have really made me connect with Mesmur, and makes me look forward to whatever's waiting in store for the character.</p> <p>Something about 3774-2432 feels very different than how she was in her original file, but I think it's explained pretty well too. In fact, I think it makes it just a bit more painful that she go back to being the way she was before. Well done.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
